title: P7  What can I do if my phone does not have sufficient storage
answer:
lIf you have inserted a microSD card into your phone, move your photos, songs, videos, and other files to the microSD card. 

![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=35558)![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=35559)


 lClean your phone storage. 

 Go to **Phone Manager**, touch **Storage cleaner**, and follow the onscreen instructions to perform a smart scan, and clear the application cache, system trash files, applications not in use and their installation packages, and large files, such as videos.
